flowchart TD
    A([Start: generateSchedule]) --> B[Sort tasks by time using tasks.time]
    B --> C[i = 0]
    C --> D{i < tasks.length - 1?}
    D -->|Yes| E{isConflict task i , task i+1 ?}
    E -->|Conflict Found| F[Halt algorithm\nReturn conflicting task i and task i+1 to client]
    F --> Z([End: generateSchedule])
    E -->|No Conflict| G[i = i + 1]
    G --> D
    D -->|No| H[Populate Schedule.tasks with sorted tasks]
    H --> I["Build Schedule.description
    ─────────────────
    For each task:
    • Date / Time
    • Pet name
    • Task title
    • Duration (mins)"]
    I --> J[Return new Schedule]
    J --> Z